HEADWORD: Strengthening
<hw>Strength"en*ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>That strengthens; giving or
increasing strength.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Strength"en*ing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Strengthening plaster</b></col> <fld>(Med.)</fld>, <cd>a
plaster containing iron, and supposed to have tonic
effects.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strengthful</ent>⟦br⟧
